    "description": "将您的管理技能放到严峻的考验中，<strong>证明自己是古希腊城市的出色统治者</strong>。在您的旅程中，您将面临许多挑战、意外事件和充满希望的机会。做出影响世界的决策，指挥您的臣民，建造壮丽的建筑，使您的波利斯成为整个古代世界最辉煌的地方！<strong>希腊建筑师：序幕</strong>，作为完整游戏的简化版本，是练习管理技能并学习基本游戏机制的绝佳方式。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特点：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>数十种不同的建筑物<br></li><li>广泛的管理和决策系统<br></li><li>随机事件和天气条件<br></li><li>贸易、政治和战争系统<br></li><li>老派的城市建设游戏玩法与现代元素</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147110/extras/82c3ab4980350b56ed7c32d78f8e6902.webp?t=1771358189\" width=600 height=11 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147110/extras/2c2bba73b02e5b479ed341d96570782d.webp?t=1771358189\" width=617 height=63 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147110/extras/6ad62b85481caf421c9a0d20ed195cc8.poster.avif?t=1771358189\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147110/extras/6ad62b85481caf421c9a0d20ed195cc8.webm?t=1771358189\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147110/extras/6ad62b85481caf421c9a0d20ed195cc8.mp4?t=1771358189\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>精确规划您的波利斯-制定自己精心设计的城市布局并建立不间断的生产链。从您可用的<strong>数十种不同的建筑物</strong>中进行选择，并决定哪些建筑物最适合您忠诚的臣民。在住宅区、行政机构、车间、服务建筑物和军事设施之间保持平衡，以确保您的城市稳定、动态发展。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147110/extras/82c3ab4980350b56ed7c32d78f8e6902.webp?t=1771358189\" width=600 height=11 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147110/extras/8f3ee3f4a9bfa16d30657a4e23ed75f0.webp?t=1771358189\" width=617 height=63 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147110/extras/91c846689f1cd921471d156e87333e7c.poster.avif?t=1771358189\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147110/extras/91c846689f1cd921471d156e87333e7c.webm?t=1771358189\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147110/extras/91c846689f1cd921471d156e87333e7c.mp4?t=1771358189\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>做出重大决策，管理您城市生活的各个方面。设置您的税收，建立新的贸易路线，占领资源丰富的地区，增加您帝国的人口，应对不可预测的事件，或成为当地的军事力量。<strong>您的统治方式完全取决于您！</strong> 关心您市民的需求，保障他们的安全并确保他们的福祉。如果失败，您的波利斯将很快遭受骚乱、瘟疫或迅速的移民。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147110/extras/82c3ab4980350b56ed7c32d78f8e6902.webp?t=1771358189\" width=600 height=11 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147110/extras/dadf351e118929e08b905aa8626723d2.webp?t=1771358189\" width=617 height=63 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147110/extras/fe3f087907e9dae0d757f497cc6cd12e.poster.avif?t=1771358189\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147110/extras/fe3f087907e9dae0d757f497cc6cd12e.webm?t=1771358189\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147110/extras/fe3f087907e9dae0d757f497cc6cd12e.mp4?t=1771358189\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>只有良好而明智的政策才能鼓励本地人口在您的城市定居。证明自己是高效的统治者，将您的小省级城镇变成一个<strong>巨大的大都市</strong>，在整个辉煌的希腊都知道！如果成功，您的城市将因其精英、一流社会、惊人的财富、壮丽的建筑和卓越的军事力量而闻名。但要小心……您的竞争对手不会闲着！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2147110/extras/82c3ab4980350b56ed7c32d78f8e6902.webp?t=1771358189\" width=600 height=11 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >将希腊建筑师添加到您的愿望清单！</h2>",
